    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 26,300₽ | 物品价值: 11,630 | Mechanic报价: 6,513₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 27,802₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级2 < 30,305₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > A Friend From the East @ 莲花\n\nAPB 手枪（俄语“消音自动手枪”的缩写；GRAU 编号：6P13）是斯捷奇金自动手枪的消音版本，多支俄罗斯特种部队均有装备。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 26,300₽ | 物品价值: 11,630 | Mechanic报价: 6,513₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 27,802₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级2 < 30,305₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > A Friend From the East @ 莲花\n\nThe APB pistol (Avtomatícheskiy Pistolét Besshúmnyy - \"Silenced Automatic Pistol\", GRAU Index - 6P13) is a silenced version of the Stechkin machine pistol, widely used by different Russian special forces."
